asset.hookText:
Galaxy Round Unboxing 

Negri Electronics: http://nel.ec/NEGRTB 

We recently received a Samsung Galaxy Round from the kind folks at Negri Electronics. It's the first phone to hit the market with a curved screen, though LG recently announced the G Flex which offers a similar design. In this video we unbox the Galaxy Round, which itself is a rare handset that's only being sold unlocked internationally, though you may find it on a carrier in South Korea.
